hey, this is jessica's n ryan's new livejournal. we got bored n decided to make one for the both of us!!! since we both hang out with each other so damn much, i think it would be alright because were usually doin somthing... this whole weekend was alot of fun. wednesday we went to the whalers game. it was alot of fun. we went seat hoppin n we picked this seat pretty close to the glass, where we made some new friends(thanks to jessica). everyone was yelling stuff at the players and jessica just goes "BE CAREFUL!!". the guy infront of us just turns around n looks at her and hes like "be careful?" me n my dad started cracking up so bad. because she sounded just like a hockey mom. thursday was thanksgiving. i had to go to my cousins(witch wasnt alot of fun) jessica went to her step-sister's. and when i came home later i went over there too n joined some of her family. their all really nice people. jaden started beating up jessica with a chicken leg cuz hes a little on the wild side. but it was all still fun. we hung out at my house friday, we were gonna go see a movie(like usual) but we dicided not to. we jsut hung out at my house n then went to hers later that night n watched a movie. saturday we didnt hang out, but sunday(today)we did. we put up the x-mas tree and hung out with my dad. annnnnnnd that was pretty much it! nothing too crazy cuz were not really crazy people! good night

-ryan
